== PVP-Arena

A PVP experience enhancing plugin.

-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

=== Features

* Multiple arenas
* Battlefield regions
* Customisable classes
* Player-state saving
* Arena regions
* In-game config access
* Arena temp-disable
* Leaderboards
* Spawn protection
* Flag colouring
* Inventory drops
* Announcements
* Arena end timer

-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

=== Functions

* Enhancing PVP experience

-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

=== Dependecies

* CraftBukkit Beta 1.2.3-R0.2

==== Optional

* Vault
* a SuperPerms compatible Permissions system
* iConomy 5/6

-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

=== How to install

* Place in plugins folder
* Configure if you wish to
* Done!

